nt:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:inherit;color:rgb(204,0,0);text=
-decoration:none">this=C2=A0</a><a href=3D"http://www.chinagfw.org/2014/11/=
goagent.html" style=3D"margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;font-family:inheri=
t;font-size:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-stretch:in=
herit;line-height:inherit;color:rgb(204,0,0);text-decoration:none">p</a>oin=
t. In the statement, he stated that he has received no money to develop GoA=
gent, provided no circumvention service, nor asserted any political view.</=
p><p style=3D"margin:0.5em 0px 1.3em;padding:0px;border:0px;font-family:inh=
erit;font-size:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-stretch=
:inherit;line-height:21px">Phus Lu=E2=80=99s caution at that time was promp=
