ght:inherit;color:rgb(204,0,0);text-decoration:none">=E2=80=9Cnetwork sover=
eignty=E2=80=9D</a>=C2=A0(Art. 25). It seems that is already being interpre=
ted to include the creators of circumvention software. A sweeping=C2=A0<a h=
